## Districts intentionally excluded

- Pierce County districts (Sumner-Bonney Lake, Puyallup, Tacoma, Bethel,
  University Place, Clover Park, Steilacoom, Peninsula, Carbonado,
  Eatonville, Orting, White River, Dieringer) - except Fife which has
  small King overlap.
- Kitsap County districts - none touch the in-scope ZIP universe.
- Whatcom / Skagit / Island districts - except Stanwood-Camano which
  includes Camano (Island County).
